Author: CommandrGylbertAdama
Text: Same. It's like a punch in the gut though. Such an incredible community, now dispersed.

Author: ArkhamBrothers
Text: I miss it every day. It was such a habit to type “ProED” in the search bar that I still do it after years of searching it daily. Ugh. Rip.   Glad you’ve been doing okay OP. Me too, me too.
